caller_intent: The caller needs to pay an overdue auto insurance bill to prevent cancellation and is seeking assistance to resolve the payment issue.
resolution_steps: Agent confirmed the caller's intent to pay an overdue bill.
Agent asked for policy type (auto) and carrier (National General).
Agent noted the policy appears canceled and offered to transfer to another agent for resolution.
summary: James Gilman contacted Alliance Insurance to resolve an overdue auto insurance payment with National General. The agent confirmed the policy was canceled and offered to transfer him to a specialist for further assistance.
